PrecisAcceptance of a DESIGNATION wherein the BLUEBERRY RIVER BAND OF INDIANS (a) surrenders, for a term of 99 years, some 3.7 hectares of Blueberry River Indian Reserve No. 205, in British Columbia, for the purpose of granting an easement for a pipeline right-of-way, and (b) extends the duration of the surrender (designation) it made in 1986.
